text: "Love Will Never Do (Without You)" is a 1990 hit single from Janet Jackson. The song was Jackson's fifth #1 single on the Billboard Hot 100. The song was from her record Rhythm Nation 1814. The song was released in October 1990. The song reached #19 on the Billboard Year-End Hot 100 of 1991. It was certified gold by the Recording Industry Association of America. ==References== Category:1990 songs Category:Janet Jackson songs Category:Billboard Hot 100 number one songs
